{"type":"message","id":"2c8514e1","parentId":"7b6228fa","timestamp":"2026-03-31T06:01:37.292Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我现在理解了任务：\n\n1. 这是一个每天下午2点的股票分析推送任务\n2. 脚本会运行 `stock_analysis_100.py` 进行分析\n3. 分析结果会保存到 `stock_analysis_results.json`\n4. 然后会格式化并发送到QQ（因为是qqbot通道）\n\n我看到：\n- `stock_analysis_results.json` 是14:00生成的最新数据（包含12只股票）\n- `stock_push_message.txt` 是上午10点的消息（这是旧的）\n\n现在我需要：\n1. 运行股票分析脚本（或者直接使用已有的14:00数据）\n2. 生成下午2点的推送消息\n3. 发送到QQ\n\n但是根据cron任务的说明：\"Return your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself.\"\n\n所以我不应该自己发送消息，而应该返回摘要。但问题是，我需要生成消息内容。让我检查一下脚本是如何工作的。\n\n根据 `stock_analysis_push_2pm.py`，它会：\n1. 运行 stock_analysis_100.py\n2. 读取 stock_analysis_results.json\n3. 格式化TOP 10股票\n4. 保存到 stock_push_message.txt\n\n现在stock_analysis_results.json的数据时间是14:00（和当前时间一致），所以分析已经完成了。\n\n我将准备运行脚本生成最终的推送消息，确保符合下午2点的时间要求。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_88f3b2726843406987576737","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python stock_analysis_push_2pm.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":3810,"output":626,"cacheRead":14482,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18918,"cost":{"input":0.002286,"output":0.0013772,"cacheRead":0.0015930200000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005256220000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774936878533}}
